item.LogMessage: iterate through productview xml files and migrate to newer version
item.action:
function UpgradeFiles(ConfigDir1,ConfigDir2) File1 = ConfigDir1 & "\productview\productview.xml"
set aConfig = CreateObject("Metratech.MTConfig.1") set aPropSet = aConfig.ReadConfiguration(File1,false)
bDone = false aVerString = "http://localhost/validation/productviewdefXML_1_0.xsd" set aXmlTrans = CreateObject("XmlTranslator.clsXmlTranslator")
while(not bDone) szFile = "" On Error resume next szFile = aPropSet.NextStringWithName("filename") On error goto 0 if szFile <> "" then
szFile = ConfigDir1 & "\productview\" & szFile
wscript.echo szFile call aXmlTrans.TranslateToLatestVersion(CStr(aVerString),CStr(szFile),CStr(szFile))
else bDone = true end if wend end function
